		   		<h1>About me</h1>	
		   		<h3>So, who am I?</h3>	
   						</div>    			
		   					<div class="circle_for_indu_photo">
									<img width="186" height="250" src="pic4_Indu.png" alt="Photo of Indu" class="img-circle" style="float:left; margin:0 40px 0 0;">
								</div>				
     							<p>I'm a UX Designer with a research & practical background in designing the user experience, usability testing and persuasive design, including working on the <a href="http://www.brl.ac.uk/researchprojects/mobiservproject.aspx">MOBISERV</a> research project at the <a href="http://www.brl.ac.uk/">BRL (Bristol Robotics Laboratory).</a> With an MSc (merit) Software Development (IT) degree from UWE, I have a passion for good design. Love a supportive UX/tech community and co-organise a local <a href="https://twitter.com/SW_UX">UX</a> group. More recently, I'm part of the team that organises <a href="http://www.accessiblebristol.org.uk/">Accessible Bristol</a>, encouraging learning/access for all, regardless of background.</p>  							
     							<h3>Designing User Journey's</h3>		
     							<div class="circle_for_design">
     							<!--<div id="circle_1">-->	
   				 				<img width="186" height="250" src="iteration_egs.jpg" alt="Iteration examples" class="img-circle" style="float:left; margin:0 40px 0 0;">
   	   					</div> 
									<p>I have an eye for detail and provide design that is both engaging and usable. From research on your users, I design the information architecture producing functional wireframes/prototypes. Involving users in the design process, I ensure usability for websites/apps. Designs I refine until I know they meet both your system and your users requirements. Experience of a wide range of wireframing, illustrator and image editor packages, use Axure RP Pro 7 on a day-to-day basis.</p>
   	   			   	<div class="circle_for_user_testing">	
   	   			   		<h3>User Testing</h3>	
   	   			   		<!--<div id="circle_1">-->
   								<img width="186" height="250" src="user_testing_photo.jpg" alt="User testing" class="img-circle" style="float:left; margin:0 40px 0 0;">
   	   					</div>	
									<p>With user research and usability/user testing, I gather evidence for design decisions, giving an understanding as to how users will interact with the design.</p>		
   	   			 		<div class="circle_for_development">
   	   						<h3>Development</h3>	
   	   						<!--<div id="circle_1">-->	
   								<img width="186" height="250" src="bbc_micro_assembly_listing.png" alt="BBC Micro assembly listing" class="img-circle" style="float:left; margin:0 60px 0 0;">
   	   					</div> 
									<p>I adapt to problem-solving. From the usability research/test findings I develop websites/mobile apps, incorporating accessibility and responsive build. Used Java, Python programming languages; MySQL; JSON; Server side: LAMP; Web development: Ruby on Rails, JavaScript, JQuery, HTML5 (W3C standards compliant), CSS3, Drupal 7 and I'm adaptable to others. Find me on GitHub.</p><a href="https://github.com/InduKaila"><span title="I'm on GitHub"><img src="Octocat.png" alt="github_icon" width="70" height="70"></span></a>			
